--- PREVENT XCom from phoning home: ---
* Add the following lines to the bottom of the hosts file

	C:\Windows\System32\drivers\etc\hosts.txt

# Prevent XCOM Phone Home
127.0.0.1 prod.xcom.firaxis.com
127.0.0.1 prod.xcom-ew.firaxis.com

# (XCOM 2012)
ALL: prod.xcom.firaxis.com
ALL: 65.118.245.165

# (XCOM EW 2012)
ALL: prod.xcom-ew.firaxis.com
ALL: 65.118.245.139
